high_descs: Turn left and face the sink on your right.
Take the knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn right and face the counter in front of you.
Slice the bread on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the microwave above the sink on your right.
Place the knife in the microwave in front of you.
Turn right and face the counter in front of you.
Take a bread slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the microwave above the sink on your right.
Heat up the bread slice in the microwave in front of you and take it out.
Turn around and face the fridge to your right.
Place the bread in the fridge in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place warm bread in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the sink on your right.
Pick up the knife on the counter in front of the two sinks.
Turn to your right and go to the counter to the left of the stove, across the room.
Cut the loaf of bread on the counter in to slices.
Turn around and go across the kitchen to the microwave above the sink, on your right.
Place the knife in the microwave, above the sink.
Turn to your right and go across the kitchen, back to the counter where the sliced bread is.
Pick up one of the slices of bread from the counter.
Turn around and go back across the kitchen to the microwave, above the sink.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the slice of bread from the microwave.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator on your right.
Place the slice of bread in the refrigerator, on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the microwave and a warm slice of bread in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Go to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife in front of the sink.
Go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Slice the loaf of bread on the counter.
Go back across the room to the microwave above the sink.
Put the butter knife in the microwave.
Move to the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Go to the microwave above the stove.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Take the hot bread to the fridge.
Put the slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm slice of bread in the fridge.
